OL,3,CGlasgow student took own life after
OL,4,Cbeing falsely told he had failed his
OL,5,Cdegree
OL,7,FThe mother of a Glasgow student who
OL,8,Ftook his own life after being
OL,9,Fincorrectly told he had failed his
OL,10,Fdegree has said her son had been
OL,11,F"failed" by the university.
OL,13,FEthan Scott Brown, 23, was due to
OL,14,Fgraduate in December 2024 after
OL,15,Fstudying geography at the University
OL,16,Fof Glasgow.
