OL,3,CGlasgow student took own life after
OL,4,Cbeing falsely told he had failed his
OL,5,Cdegree
OL,7,FHowever, his family said that in
OL,8,FSeptember 2024, the university told
OL,9,Fhim that he had not been awarded a
OL,10,Fgrade for one course and would
OL,11,Ftherefore not be eligible to graduate
OL,12,Fwith an Honours degree.
OL,14,FThe family said that as a result, he
OL,15,Fwent on to take his own life on
OL,16,FDecember 13 2024, the day he should
OL,17,Fhave been graduating.
