OL,3,CGlasgow student took own life after
OL,4,Cbeing falsely told he had failed his
OL,5,Cdegree
OL,7,FHis family, from Coatbridge in North
OL,8,FLanarkshire, believe there has been a
OL,9,F"systemic failure" at the university
OL,10,Fand are calling for answers about
OL,11,Fwhether other students at the
OL,12,Funiversity are affected and may have
OL,13,Fbeen wrongly told they failed.
OL,15,FThe university has admitted there was
OL,16,Fa "tragic error" around Ethan's marks
OL,17,Fand expressed its deepest sympathies,
OL,18,Fbut said the issue was an isolated
OL,19,Fincident.
