OL,7,F"We seek justice for Ethan in the hope
OL,8,Fthat other students and their families
OL,9,Fdo not have to experience the pain
OL,10,Fthat myself and my family will have to
OL,11,Flive with forever."
OL,13,FThe family's solicitor, Aamer Anwar,
OL,14,Fsaid the family also want to know
OL,15,F"whether this systemic failure would
OL,16,Fever have been identified had Ethan
OL,17,Fnot died and his family had not fought
OL,18,Ffor answers".
