OL,7,FMr Anwar said the family also wish to
OL,8,Fraise "serious concerns" about the
OL,9,Fwellbeing support offered to
OL,10,Fstruggling students by the University
OL,11,Fof Glasgow.
OL,13,FEthan reported difficulties with his
OL,14,Fmental health to the university.
OL,16,FHowever, his family say that no
OL,17,Fsupport was offered.
