OL,7,FAsked whether there will be any legal
OL,8,Faction against the university, Mr
OL,9,FAnwar said: "At the moment the family
OL,10,Fare considering all options."
OL,12,FThe University of Glasgow said once
OL,13,FEthan's family had contacted them,
OL,14,Fthey conducted a report chaired by a
OL,15,Frecently retired senior professor,
OL,16,Fwith the results shared with the
OL,17,Ffamily.
